# DealDrops — deals.akibsaify.in

> Daily Deal Drops — curated Amazon India deals with price history, MRP comparisons, and category filters. Updated daily with verified discounts of 30% or more.

## What is DealDrops?
DealDrops is an Indian deals website that scans Amazon India every few hours to find the best deals across electronics, fashion, home & kitchen, grocery, and travel. Every deal is verified with real price comparisons showing deal price, MRP, discount percentage, and exact savings in Indian Rupees (INR). We only list deals with a minimum 30% discount — no inflated MRPs, no expired offers.

