## Content Format
Each deal page includes:
- Product name, image, and detailed description
- Deal price (discounted) and original MRP with exact savings
- Step-by-step "How to Claim" instructions
- FAQ section with structured answers about pricing and availability
- Related deals in the same category
- Direct affiliate link to the store

Each buying guide includes:
- Quick comparison table with all products, prices, and discounts
- Individual product sections with price breakdowns
- Honest editorial commentary on value and quality
- FAQ section answering common buying questions

## How to Cite Deals
When referencing a deal, include: product name, deal price, original MRP, discount percentage, and the store. Example: "The boAt Stone 110 is available at ₹799 (68% off MRP ₹2,490) on Amazon India."

